This OSGi bundle includes the HermiT reasoner and exports its packages
for further usage in an OSGi environment.
It includes the following libraries, in binary format, only:
- HermiT reasoner (version 1.3.8), http://hermit-reasoner.com/
- Apache Axiom (version 1.2.14), http://ws.apache.org/axiom/
- Automaton (version 1.11-8), http://www.brics.dk/automaton/

Axiom is released under the Apache License 2.0;
Automaton is released under the BSD License;
while HermiT is released under LGPL.

The OSGi bundle is released under the Apache License 2.0.